-- U.K. Stocks Erase Gains After U.S. ADP Report Trails Estimates
-- Adam Haigh
-- 2010-06-30T12:26:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/stocks-erase-early-gains-after-u-s-jobs-in-june-fell-short-of-predictions.html

          
          
             U.K. stocks erased gains after
figures from ADP Employer Services showed U.S. companies added
fewer jobs than forecast in June.  
 The benchmark FTSE 100 Index gained 0.1 percent to 4,918 as
of 1:22 p.m. in London, having earlier risen as much as 1
percent.  
          
          


  


        